# Groq API Configuration (FREE TIER: 14,400 requests/day PER KEY)
# Get your FREE API key from https://console.groq.com/keys
# Support MULTIPLE keys (comma-separated) for higher limits:
# Example: GROQ_API_KEY=key1,key2,key3
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-groq-api-key-here

# Optional: Override default model (default: llama3-8b-8192)
# Available free models: llama-3.1-8b-instant, llama-3.1-70b-versatile, mixtral-8x7b-32768
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.1-8b-instant

# Optional: Override max tokens (default: 1000)
# GROQ_MAX_TOKENS=1000

# Optional: Override temperature (default: 0.7)
# GROQ_TEMPERATURE=0.7

# IMPORTANT: Add these environment variables to Vercel:
# 1. Go to your Vercel project dashboard
# 2. Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add GROQ_API_KEY with your free API key(s) from https://console.groq.com/keys
#    - For multiple keys, separate with commas: key1,key2,key3
#    - Each key gives you 14,400 requests/day
# 4. Deploy again after adding the variable
#
# Example with 3 keys: 43,200 requests/day total!
